ComicInfo.Summary:
As David suffers in Heaven and Heather struggles on Earth, their separate troubles lead to one life-and-death question: "What is L-Meat?" Pplus, a member of Hashtag: Danger lies dead! Aren't you shocked? Plus bonus AHOY illustrated text stories! Painted cover by Richard Williams (MAD).
